## ğŸ”§ Building from Source

### Prerequisites

- Rust 1.70+
- Python 3.7+
- maturin (`pip install maturin`)

### Build

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/loonghao/ipckit.git
cd ipckit

# Build Python package
maturin develop --release

# Run tests
pytest tests/
cargo test
```

